{"tid":2348072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡連任 韓丟官 天下圍中助台走向國際","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T13:30:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf8d0f50b51c79d6e2aa9ddf21fec873ec42ae5","tid":2348072,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201231/X5H3476XBZFBJMZYH3FRPY6O3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201231%2FX5H3476XBZFBJMZYH3FRPY6O3A%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=8fc2cdac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201231%2FX5H3476XBZFBJMZYH3FRPY6O3A%2F&h=7f5706bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201231/X5H3476XBZFBJMZYH3FRPY6O3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蔡連任 韓丟官 天下圍中助台走向國際<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F_V_XvjSYA-VhmtHzxlyqvrWoLs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EBK44UF5PVGUZBYJDYLW2VDGKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF_V_XvjSYA-VhmtHzxlyqvrWoLs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEBK44UF5PVGUZBYJDYLW2VDGKY.jpg&h=f1b34607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■韓國瑜總統敗選兼被罷免高雄市長，成為大輸家。<br />\n<br />\n【兩岸寒冬】今年的兩岸關係，隨蔡英文於年初成功連任總統後，便可預視雙方官方交流會跌入谷底。相反美台則迎來前所未有的蜜月期，除了多位美方高官接連訪台，台灣今年受天下圍中浪潮影響，頻頻在國際社會曝光，大大幫助台灣未來的發言權。<br />\n<br />\n受益於香港反送中運動，蔡英文於1月11日擊敗國民黨的韓國瑜成功連任，民進黨續掌立法院。蔡在勝選後指：「台灣已經是獨立的國家。」為今年續冷的兩岸關係定調。落選的韓國瑜於6月，遭公投通過罷免高雄市長職務，成為台灣史上首位被罷免市長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OQeGZ7Yp8LOB_EF701ywG6K5pFs=/830x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SGFXH4TY2VBVVLSIZVTPDUYTJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOQeGZ7Yp8LOB_EF701ywG6K5pFs%3D%2F830x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSGFXH4TY2VBVVLSIZVTPDUYTJI.jpg&h=d1ede1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡英文連任總統後，外交上大打國際牌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美捷高官訪台 李登輝逝世<br />\n<br />\n民進黨「全面執政」後，美台關係大幅度升溫。賴清德2月以「民間人士」身份訪美，成為首位訪問華府的台灣候任副總統。8月起，美國衞生部長阿扎爾、國務次卿克拉奇、海軍印太情報總指揮官斯圖德曼先後訪台，美台軍售頻繁。此外，捷克參議院議長維特齊8月底亦率團訪台，是歷來訪台最高級現任捷克政治人物。維特齊在台立法院上以中文表示「我是台灣人」，藉此向台灣人民表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n但遺憾的是，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共機頻擾台 武統論再起<br />\n<br />\n美台關係升溫亦意味兩岸關係轉冷。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，兩岸要重返「習馬會」年代的蜜月期恐難復見。"},{"pid":"933ef3f9989d755d86fb574c9c0d209c5bf404ab","tid":2348072,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}